{"tid":579134,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"借你耳仔用下呀麻煩晒 之 如果我不曾來過","createTime":"2018-03-03T10:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T07:49:35.000Z","uid":131223,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44c2bb4c2bccd26e6debad970ec99d1fcbcf78b4","tid":579134,"uid":131223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"細個唔識世界，係電台最光輝既年代我冇一放學就開住個收音機黎煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n到大個左先搵番少爺占啲廣播劇黎聽(八王子, 好天氣, 小小雪, 四點水etc)<br />\r\n仲瘋狂到要走去中央圖書館搵文字版黎睇<br />\r\n於是就萌生左寫劇既念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"> 我寫野係勁差 公開試攞好低分<br />\r\n</span></span><br />\r\n可能人越大就越想番去以前<br />\r\n想試下有冇可能做到一啲有人鍾意聽既劇<br />\r\n咁啱比我遇到一班唔計較既朋友幫我錄<br />\r\n又咁啱好彩順利完成左錄音部分<br />\r\n第一次做廣播劇，好多錯漏，而係我能力範圍下<br />\r\n都盡量將啲錯處解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錯左求唔好hi我</span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n自問把聲非常唔好聽<br />\r\n我諗呢個係發夢做電台既人既悲劇黎<br />\r\n希望各位巴絲聽完可以比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n咁我下個劇就可以改善做得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n個劇仍在後製過程中<br />\n每星期會upload新既一集<br />\n如果你地睇字睇到攰<br />\n搭車又唔想聽歌，咪當聽下我噏廢話囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事大綱：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n自命愛情美滿的Giyan，在事業和愛情皆在高峰的階段痛失兩者。在公司，她揹上黑鍋被辭退；在家裏，她更漸漸被男友Nate冷落，決意挽回這段感情的她，第一步是去買煙？<br />\r\n另一邊廂的Mike，與女友Cora相處表面幸福，實際上Cora是個控制狂，她嘗試控制著他的生活，使得Mike喘不過氣，每晚在和女友視訊後都會偷偷在家附近流連。<br />\r\n就在某個晚上，Giyan和Mike在便利店相遇，兩個互不相識的生命，從那晚起便糾纏不清⋯⋯<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n第一集 - 我們由這裡開始<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-661207061/ep1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-661207061%2Fep1&d=mNAIbFpH%2FXaHed9whc5rudibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9c15109b\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-661207061/ep1</a>"},{"pid":"1a38b709f5793f719ed56e67a84226a0ac284df6","tid":579134,"uid":7353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e117b8b3d1658e4c07308ec60e46b91faa5ab84f","tid":579134,"uid":131223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a38b709f5793f719ed56e67a84226a0ac284df6","tid":579134,"uid":7353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:51:45.000Z","msg":"感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f050f33ea3a30947b4c3116548818011c1d4d5","tid":579134,"uid":167067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"正個皮先<br />\n好似幾得意"},{"pid":"f2bb4fb5d935ab568352483338bd4cb24357cdac","tid":579134,"uid":131223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9f050f33ea3a30947b4c3116548818011c1d4d5","tid":579134,"uid":167067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"正個皮先<br />\n好似幾得意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:49:35.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}